song.title: Holidays '93
song.info: it's a tune for music competition at: polish autum'93 in poznan. all drums and chords sounds by me, from my roland jv-30. 3 samples used in it (14,16,1e) has been done by lizardking / atz. greetings to all friends and contacts. playing time: 04:10 tune composed durning august'93.
